# E-commerce Store Project Overview

This is a Next.js 14 e-commerce application with TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, and Prisma ORM. The project follows a modern, modular architecture with clear separation of concerns.

## Main Entry Points
- [app/layout.tsx](mdc:app/layout.tsx) - Root layout component that wraps all pages
- [app/(root)/page.tsx](mdc:app/(root)/page.tsx) - Homepage component
- [auth.ts](mdc:auth.ts) - Authentication configuration using NextAuth.js
- [middleware.ts](mdc:middleware.ts) - Next.js middleware for route protection

## Key Configuration Files
- [next.config.ts](mdc:next.config.ts) - Next.js configuration
- [tailwind.config.ts](mdc:tailwind.config.ts) - Tailwind CSS configuration
- [prisma/schema.prisma](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma) - Database schema

## Directory Structure
- `/app` - Next.js app router pages and layouts
- `/components` - Reusable UI components
- `/lib` - Utility functions and shared logic
- `/hooks` - Custom React hooks
- `/types` - TypeScript type definitions
- `/prisma` - Database schema and migrations
- `/public` - Static assets
- `/email` - Email templates and handlers
- `/db` - Database utilities and configurations

